public class Frog
extends MovableActor
Frog is a MovableActor that is controlled as the player character.

    • Frog

      public Frog()
      Constructor initializes a new Frog that can be drawn on the screen. The Frog automatically uses the default Frog image and size, while also being positioned at the constant starting coordinates.
